2d53faf5ac33e7f004cbdc9a8b6d3642f967f330
2026-05-21
feat: HeaderComponent — glass morphism + scroll reveal (#23)

Scroll threshold: visible when window.scrollY > window.innerHeight * 0.8.
Header owns the check via @HostListener('window:scroll'); all window access
guarded by isPlatformBrowser so it is a no-op during SSR.

Style: backdrop-filter blur(12px) + 80% opacity --mat-sys-surface (glass
morphism). Fades in via opacity + pointer-events CSS transition (0.3s).

Navigation simplified:
- Logo click -> /
- "About" link -> routerLink="/" fragment="about" (/#about from any route)
- Removed "Home" and "Resume" links
- Removed RouterLinkActive import (no longer needed)

AppComponent: removed pt-16 from main — header is now a floating overlay,
not a static layout element that requires reserved space at the top.

Ships 6 specs: hidden by default, visible past threshold, stays hidden below
threshold, no visibility update on server platform, logo href, About href.

Files changed:
  src/app/layout/header/header.ts
  src/app/layout/header/header.html
  src/app/layout/header/header.scss
  src/app/layout/header/header.spec.ts (new)
  src/app/app.ts

Unblocks #25 (HomeComponent scroll exit + single-page integration).
