f88afa906832984c6a6d97be4314581a0c85ea57
2026-05-21
feat: HeroSectionComponent (#22)

Adds HeroSectionComponent at src/app/pages/home/hero-section/.
Full-viewport dark section that renders HeroCanvasComponent as background
and overlays the engineer name + title from PortfolioConfig with a CTA
button that smooth-scrolls to #about.

No scroll or transition logic — HomeComponent will own the exitProgress
animation in issue #25.

scrollToAbout() is guarded by isPlatformBrowser so it is a no-op during
SSR; fragment navigation wiring (anchorScrolling) is deferred to #25.

HomeComponent updated to import HeroSectionComponent and bind techStack;
inline canvas + overlay markup removed from home.html.

Ships 7 specs: full-viewport section, name from config, title from config,
CTA button text, HeroCanvasComponent in DOM, scroll to #about in browser,
DOM not accessed on server platform.

