cdf1f5d4cdaa9a1ecaa6a8a84a8f3df27b8fa085
2026-05-21
feat: HeroCanvasComponent + TechStackConfig (#21)

Replaces StarFieldComponent with HeroCanvasComponent at
src/app/pages/home/hero-canvas/. One RAF loop, one canvas. Accepts
icons: TechIcon[] as a required signal input; parent passes
TECH_STACK_CONFIG so the animation pool is configurable.

FlyingLogo (formerly Comet) now preloads SVG images via HTMLImageElement
and draws them inside a circular clip mask with a brand-coloured glow.
Falls back to text abbreviation on load failure or before image is ready.

Three modes driven by DevicePerformanceService:
- Desktop: star field + flying logos + mouse/logo push physics
- Mobile (isLowPerf): stars + logos, push physics off, ~60% fewer stars
- prefersReducedMotion: RAF loop never started; 8 logos rendered at fixed
  positions alongside stars for a single static frame. Resize re-renders
  the static frame so the canvas stays populated after dimension changes.

Adds TechStackConfig (TechIcon[]) at src/app/pages/home/tech-stack.config.ts
with 25 entries sourced from Devicon CDN plus custom Claude and Cursor
icons at src/assets/icons/{claude,cursor}.svg.

HomeComponent updated to import HeroCanvasComponent and bind techStack.
StarFieldComponent and its spec deleted.

Ships 6 specs: canvas renders, animation loop disabled in reduced-motion,
canvas renders in low-perf mode, empty-icons no-crash, resize static
re-render, resize no-renderStatic in non-reduced mode.

Files changed:
  src/app/pages/home/hero-canvas/hero-canvas.ts
  src/app/pages/home/hero-canvas/hero-canvas.spec.ts
  src/app/pages/home/tech-stack.config.ts
